resources.string: "For fans of arabica coffee with a dark chocolate flavor profile, this product can be an option. In addition to the dark chocolate note, you will also taste notes of brown sugar and orange zest, resulting in an interesting blend of flavors. You can enjoy this arabica coffee with various brewing methods. For V 60 and Vietnamese drip, you can choose a medium grind. For french press and cold brew, choose a coarse grind. For moka pot and espresso enthusiasts, you can choose a fine grind."
